document.full_text: representative anthony weiner (d-ny), who has denied sending a lewd photo of himself to a 21-year-old female college student over his twitter account, canceled a scheduled speech on friday at the democratic party of wisconsin's state convention.
document.title: anthony weiner cancels wisconsin speech to democrats
